# PLAN: Growth — osTwin Interactive EPIC Editor & DAG Authoring (Frontend)

## Goal

Transform the plan editor from a plain textarea + read-only DAG viewer into a bidirectional authoring environment. The frontend parses EPIC markdown into a structured AST, renders it as interactive checklists and form fields, and lets users edit EPICs visually from the DAG canvas. All changes serialize back to markdown and save via the existing `POST /api/plans/{id}/save` endpoint. No backend changes required.

